name: WootStalker
0:
”Alexa, open woot stalker”
”What is for sale on home?”
”Read the monkey chat”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: woot stalker
des:
Woot Stalker lists current deal information for the daily deal site woot.com. You are able to retrieve the item, price, condition, and more for each of the main deals across all categories. Supported categories are: woot, home, sport, tools, tech, computers, shirt, sellout, and wine.

You can also read the daily monkey chat.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
